# Transforming Teaching with AI


#### Welcome! This professional learning module is designed to help you learn how to use AI to support your role as an educator.

<img src="https://images.code.org/1cd0ec71458414495502b9598efd2028-image-1639773441510.37.01 PM.png" alt="Image of AI bot" style="border-radius:40px; float: right; padding-right: 75px; height: 275px; clear: both; margin: 0 0px 0px 0;">

## In this module, you will:

* #### Learn guiding principles when using AI in an educational context.
* #### Practice how to effectively use AI tools to support various educational tasks.
* #### Assess the suitability of different AI tools and platforms for their specific teaching contexts.

